-                             *    `(48|4C) 8D 05 disp32` whose target is the bool
-                             *    getter `movzx eax,byte[rcx+disp8]; ret`
-                             *    (0F B6 41 disp8 C3) and overwrite its exact
-                             *    five-byte body with `xor eax,eax; inc eax; ret`.
